[49m[38;5;9m- 116     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m **Amazon SQS for work queue management.** Slides arrive throughout the day. A queue decouples slide arrival from processing capacity, enabling smooth scaling without dropped work.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      116[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Amazon SQS for work queue management.** Slides arrive throughout the day. A queue decouples slide arrival from processing capacity, enabling smooth scaling without dropped work. Configure a dead letter queue (DLQ) with a `maxReceiveCount` of 3 so slides that repeatedly fail processing move aside for manual investigation rather than cycling indefinitely. Monitor DLQ depth via CloudWatch alarm: a growing DLQ indicates a systemic issue (new scanner format, model degradation, infrastructure problem).
